These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-1::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: bellflower, aconite, balloon-flower, amaryllis
4 different pets are kept: cat, ferret, lizard, turtle
City: hamburg, paris, london, colone
1. the person traveling to london is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
2. the person traveling to colone is the owner of the cat##1
3. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the far left##1
4. the person who growsbellflower is on the far right##1
5. the owner of the ferret is between the person traveling to london and the person who growsaconite##2
6. the person traveling to paris is the owner of the lizard##1
7. the owner of the cat is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Flower        | balloon-flower | amaryllis  | aconite | bellflower  |
| Pet         | turtle    | ferret  | cat       | lizard     |
| City   | london     | hamburg | colone       | paris |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, drawing, magic-tricks, reading
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, italian, indonesian, pakistani
4 different games are played: backgammon, domino, whist, mah-jongg
1. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the far left##1
2. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1
3. the person playing domino is on the far left##1
4. the person playing mah-jongg is between the pakistani and the person who's hobby is reading##2
5. the pakistani is the person playing domino##1
6. the australian is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
7. the indonesian is the person playing whist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3     |      4       |
| Hobby         | drawing | chess    | reading  | magic-tricks |
| Nationality   | pakistani  | australian  | italian   | indonesian    |
| Game         | domino | mah-jongg | backgammon | whist      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-3::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, airplane, snowmobile, trike
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, cooking, gardening, photography
City: hannover, marseilles, boston, berlin
1. the person traveling to marseilles is between the person traveling to berlin and the person driving the airplane##2
2. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the person traveling to hannover##1
3. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
4. the person driving the snowmobile is on the far right##1
5. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the far left##1
6. the person traveling to hannover is on the right of the person driving the van##1
7. the person traveling to boston is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |     3      |     4     |
| Transport      | airplane | trike         | van   | snowmobile    |
| Hobby         | cooking | photography | collecting | gardening |
| City   | boston   | marseilles        | berlin      | hannover   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: filmmaking, dominod-games, photography, chess
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, cycling, skateboarding, tennis
4 different games are played: canasta, domino, monopoly, whist
1. the person playing monopoly is on the far left##1
2. the person playing canasta is between the person playing whist and the person who's hobby is chess##2
3. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
4. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
5. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
6. the person playing whist is between the person who's sport is cricket and the person playing domino##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |     3      |   4    |
| Hobby   | chess        | dominod-games   | filmmaking | photography |
| Sport         | skateboarding | cricket | cycling    | tennis |
| Game     | monopoly       | canasta     | whist       | domino    |

