The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, puzzles, sudoku, woodworking
City: san-francisco, boston, nizza, venice
1. the person traveling to venice is between the person who's birthday is in december and the person who's birthday is in november##2
2. the person traveling to venice is the person who's birthday is in august##1
3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the far right##1
4. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
5. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the right of the person traveling to nizza##1
6. the person traveling to nizza is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
7. the person traveling to venice is between the person traveling to nizza and the person who's hobby is gardening##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |      3      |     4      |
| Birthday   | december | august      | november       | september   |
| Hobby      | gardening   | puzzles  | woodworking | sudoku     |
| City      | boston     | venice | nizza        | san-francisco |

