.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-6::.
There 4 different types of food: cherry, cranberry, cucumber, mango
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, airplane, roller, helicopter
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, june, march, september
1. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
2. the person eating cherry is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
3. the person eating cherry is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
4. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person eating cranberry##1
5. the person driving the boat is between the person driving the helicopter and the person who's birthday is in march##2
6. the person eating cranberry is between the person eating cherry and the person eating cucumber##2
7. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person driving the roller##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |   3    |     4      |
| Food    | cucumber | cranberry  | cherry | mango      |
| Transport   | roller  | helicopter  | boat | airplane |
| Birthday   | september | november | june | march     |

