.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-7::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, november, august, january
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: drama, epic, mystery, spy
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, van, airplane, taxi
1. the person driving the taxi is the person watching epic movies##1
2. the person driving the airplane is the person watching drama movies##1
3. the person watching mystery movies is on the far left##1
4. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
5. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
6. the person who's birthday is in november is between the person watching epic movies and the person watching mystery movies##2
7. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Birthday          | august  | november    | january | may  |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | spy       | epic        | drama    |
| Transport         | van | boat | taxi  | airplane |

