.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-8::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, soul, electronic, rock
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, crime, spy, western
The people use 4 different means of transport: ship, quad-bike, jet-ski, subway
1. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
2. the person watching crime movies is between the person driving the subway and the fan of soul##2
3. the fan of electronic is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
4. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
5. the person watching western movies is on the right of the fan of rock##1
6. the fan of electronic is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3    |      4      |
| Music-Genre         | rock  | soul | electronic | country |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy  | western | crime   | spy         |
| Transport           | ship | jet-ski  | quad-bike   | subway      |

