.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-9::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: documentary, disaster, time-travel, martial-arts
There are 4 different nationalities: pakistani, american, russian, turkish
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, house, salsa, techno
1. the fan of salsa is on the left of the fan of techno##1
2. the american is the person watching documentary movies##1
3. the fan of house is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
4. the russian is the person watching disaster movies##1
5. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
6. the russian is on the far right##1
7. the american is between the fan of salsa and the pakistani##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |      4      |
| Movie-Genre          | martial-arts  | documentary    | time-travel | disaster       |
| Nationality         | turkish | american | pakistani  | russian |
| Music-Genre   | salsa   | techno      | house  | ambient     |

