3. the dutch is between the turkish and the person driving the bike##2
4. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the polish##1
5. the person driving the ship is on the far right##1
6. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the polish##1
7. the person watching time-travel movies is the person driving the trike##1
8. the person watching adventure movies is the polish##1

.:: Answer ::.
