.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-11::.
4 different games are played: bridge, poker, monopoly, canasta
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, camping, puzzles, reading
House: townhouse, colonial, craftsman, farmhouse
1. the person playing poker is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
2. the craftsman house is the person playing poker##1
3. the townhouse house is between the person who's hobby is camping and the person who's hobby is puzzles##2
4. the person who's hobby is puzzles is between the townhouse house and the person playing canasta##2
5. the person who's hobby is puzzles is the farmhouse house##1
6. the person who's hobby is board-games is the colonial house##1
7. the person who's hobby is reading is the townhouse house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |    3     |     4      |
| Game    | canasta  | monopoly | bridge | poker     |
| Hobby   | board-games | puzzles   | reading  | camping    |
| House     | colonial        | farmhouse       | townhouse      | craftsman |

