.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-12::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: october, december, january, july
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, gardening, sudoku, traveling
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: bellflower, rose, poppy, daffodil
1. the person who growsrose is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
2. the person who's hobby is traveling is the person who's birthday is in january##1
3. the person who's birthday is in december is between the person who's birthday is in january and the person who's hobby is gardening##2
4. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the far left##1
5. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person who growsrose##1
6. the person who growsbellflower is on the far right##1
7. the person who growspoppy is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Birthday   | july | january     | december | october       |
| Hobby      | sudoku  | traveling | card-games  | gardening |
| Flower        | daffodil  | rose      | poppy        | bellflower      |

