.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-13::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: orange, green, grey, lilac
The people have 4 different hobbies: drawing, filmmaking, hiking, reading
House: cottage, gothic-revival, cape-cod, ranch-style
1. the person who likes lilac is on the left of the cottage house##1
2. the ranch-style house is between the person who likes grey and the person who's hobby is drawing##2
3. the person who likes green is on the right of the person who likes grey##1
4. the person who likes orange is the cape-cod house##1
5. the gothic-revival house is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
6. the person who likes lilac is the person who's hobby is hiking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |     3      |    4    |
| Color   | orange | lilac  | grey       | green   |
| Hobby      | drawing     | hiking | filmmaking | reading |
| House        | cape-cod        | ranch-style | cottage     | gothic-revival |

