.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-14::.
4 different pets are kept: goat, bird, guinea-pig, turtle
4 different games are played: domino, bridge, backgammon, billiard
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, bus, ship, trike
1. the person playing domino is the person driving the trike##1
2. the person driving the ship is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
3. the person driving the ship is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
4. the person playing billiard is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
5. the person driving the bus is between the person playing backgammon and the owner of the guinea-pig##2
6. the person driving the trike is on the far right##1
7. the person driving the bus is the owner of the turtle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Pet           | bird | turtle | guinea-pig    | goat   |
| Game   | backgammon      | bridge   | billiard | domino |
| Transport     | airplane     | bus       | ship        | trike    |

