1. the person who's birthday is in june is the person who's sport is rugby##1
2. the person who's sport is sailing is the person who's birthday is in september##1
3. the person who's birthday is in march is the owner of the fish##1
4. the person who's birthday is in june is on the far left##1
5. the person who's sport is parkour is between the owner of the goat and the person who's birthday is in march##2
6. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
7. the person who's sport is biathlon is between the person who's sport is sailing and the person who's sport is parkour##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |        2        |       3        |       4        |
| Birthday   | june   | december           | march         | september      |
| Pet     | goat | hamster | fish | bird |
| Sport   | rugby     | parkour         | biathlon       | sailing        |

