.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-17::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: woodworking, traveling, dancing, camping
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, kiwi, lime, orange
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, soul, dubstep, blues
1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the far left##1
2. the person eating lime is between the person who's hobby is camping and the fan of dubstep##2
3. the fan of blues is on the right of the fan of soul##1
4. the fan of ambient is on the far right##1
5. the person eating artichoke is on the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
6. the person eating kiwi is on the right of the person eating lime##1
7. the person who's hobby is dancing is the fan of ambient##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |    2    |       3       |    4     |
| Hobby   | woodworking    | traveling | camping           | dancing |
| Food       | artichoke | lime    | kiwi          | orange   |
| Music-Genre      | dubstep  | soul   | blues | ambient  |

