.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-18::.
There are 4 different nationalities: american, canadian, german, italian
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: hip-hop, jazz, metal, soul
4 different pets are kept: cat, hedgehog, horse, mouse
1. the fan of metal is the canadian##1
2. the american is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
3. the fan of soul is on the right of the german##1
4. the american is between the fan of metal and the fan of hip-hop##2
5. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the italian##1
6. the owner of the mouse is between the canadian and the owner of the cat##2
7. the fan of soul is the owner of the mouse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |    3     |   4   |
| Nationality      | german | american | canadian     | italian   |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop | soul        | metal  | jazz  |
| Pet           | cat      | mouse         | hedgehog | horse |

