.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-19::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, bolivar, tiparillo, fonseca
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: western, mystery, action, family
The people use 4 different means of transport: roller, scooter, subway, taxi
1. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the tiparillo-smoker##1
2. the person watching family movies is the person driving the roller##1
3. the oliveros-smoker is on the far left##1
4. the person driving the subway is the fonseca-smoker##1
5. the person watching western movies is the person driving the subway##1
6. the person driving the taxi is between the person watching mystery movies and the person driving the subway##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2      |     3      |      4       |
| Cigar         | oliveros        | fonseca  | tiparillo | bolivar   |
| Movie-Genre       | family | western | action    | mystery |
| Transport   | roller        | subway     | taxi       | scooter      |

