4. the person who's birthday is in september is on the far right##1
5. the person driving the skateboard is the person watching crime movies##1
6. the person watching animation movies is between the person who's birthday is in may and the person driving the motorbike##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2    |     3     |     4      |
